      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $(a_n)$ une suite réelle positive.\nOn pose $u_n = \\frac {a_n}{(1+a_1)(1+a_2)\\dots(1+a_n)}$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\((a_n)\\)</span> une suite réelle\npositive. On pose <span class=\"math inline\">\\(u_n = \\frac\n{a_n}{(1+a_1)(1+a_2)\\dots(1+a_n)}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8d5f168d-652c-488c-a048-42fcf8d277cc",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que la série $\\sum u_n$ converge.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que la série <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum u_n\\)</span>\nconverge.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "0038333d-964b-4ca0-bf57-e686bc5e84dd",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$u_1 + \\dots + u_n = 1 - \\frac1{(1+a_1)\\dots(1+a_n)} \\le 1$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(u_1 + \\dots + u_n = 1 -\n\\frac1{(1+a_1)\\dots(1+a_n)} \\le 1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "1f071797-0502-4872-b9f4-5e3eefbdd611",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty u_n$ lorsque $a_n = \\frac 1{\\sqrt n}$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty u_n\\)</span>\nlorsque <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_n = \\frac 1{\\sqrt n}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "02f427d6-cb81-4cc2-b788-958ce13b185d",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\ln\\bigl((1+a_1)\\dots(1+a_n)\\bigr)\n              = \\sum_{k=1}^n \\ln\\left(1+\\frac1{\\sqrt k}\\right)\n              \\to +\\infty  \\Rightarrow  \\sum u_n = 1$ lorsque $n\\to\\infty$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\ln\\bigl((1+a_1)\\dots(1+a_n)\\bigr)\n              = \\sum_{k=1}^n \\ln\\left(1+\\frac1{\\sqrt k}\\right)\n              \\to +\\infty  \\Rightarrow  \\sum u_n = 1\\)</span> lorsque\n<span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\to\\infty\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ],
